HEADWORD: Ultroneous
<hw>Ul*tro"ne*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ultroneus</ets>, from <ets>ultro</ets> to the further side, on his
part, of one's own accord. See <er>Ultra-</er>.]</ety> <def>Spontaneous;
voluntary.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <au>Jer. Taylor.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Ul*tro"ne*ous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> -- <wf>Ul*tro"ne*ous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ulula</ent>⟦br⟧
